  "title": "AI 写爆款博客火出圈，主笔竟是 Claude！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652602864&idx=3&sn=5a820948bbc7e13f080a315d393757ab",
  "date": "2025-06-19 05:04:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d44ca5c6-dfd1-470e-7c45-1ff8513f7400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42643923240938164\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"2345\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505115564\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d44ca5c6-dfd1-470e-7c45-1ff8513f7400/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：英智</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">普华永道的最新研究揭秘：AI不仅没抢饭碗，还让员工创效翻三倍，数据库工程师岗位暴增2312%。从招聘到绩效，AI正重塑企业运营逻辑。AI能帮你干活，但人情味还得靠自己！</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近，Anthropic给自家AI开了个博客。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个叫「Claude Explain」的博客页面，内容主要由AI模型Claude生成。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2b3da28-736d-4a71-bd84-0ebfe481fb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"304\" data-imgfileid=\"505115290\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2b3da28-736d-4a71-bd84-0ebfe481fb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">博客包括《用Claude简化复杂代码库》这种硬核主题，旨在秀一把AI的写作能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过别误会，这可不是AI在放飞自我。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前尚不清楚Claude的原始写作内容在文章中占多大比例。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据一位发言人介绍，所有内容都得经过Anthropic的专家和编辑团队把关，他们会给初稿加上真知灼见、实际案例和背景知识。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">发言人表示，这并非是AI随意输出，编辑过程需要人类的专业知识，并且经过多次迭代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从技术角度看，「Claude Explain」展示了一种协作方式：Claude创建教育内容，团队进行审核、完善和优化。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef3292e6-c6d3-4393-1c11-4ebaf3705600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5268518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"296\" data-imgfileid=\"505115291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef3292e6-c6d3-4393-1c11-4ebaf3705600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但要是点开博客主页，估计会有点懵：欢迎来到Anthropic宇宙的小角落，Claude在这里聊各种话题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这容易让人误以为整个博客全是Claude一手包办。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Anthropic表示，做这个博客其实是想演示「人类+AI」的协作模式，先从教育内容开始试水。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就像用AI给工作</span><span leaf=\"\">「</span><span leaf=\"\">开挂</span><span leaf=\"\">」</span><span leaf=\"\">，给用户提供更多价值。我们不是要取代人，而是让专家能借助AI做更多事。接下来还会有创意写作、数据分析、商业策略这些话题。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI写内容，早就不是新鲜事了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta的小扎想开发一种端到端的AI广告工具，OpenAI搞出了专门写创意文案的模型，放话「AI能搞定95%营销人的活」。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4e3585f4-8b53-4828-0639-4299c0af3900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505115292\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4e3585f4-8b53-4828-0639-4299c0af3900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">出版商也在尝试用AI写新闻：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Gannett用AI写体育赛事总结和头条摘要，Bloomberg给文章加AI摘要；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Business Insider上周裁员21%，并力推记者用AI辅助写作；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">《纽约时报》鼓励员工用AI提供编辑建议、撰写标题，生成采访问题；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">《华盛顿邮报》正在开发一款名为Ember的AI驱动的「故事编辑器」。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5973a500-00ee-4539-d448-5cb01f527a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505115293\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5973a500-00ee-4539-d448-5cb01f527a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但现实很骨感，这些AI写稿尝试好多都翻车了——最大的毛病就是「瞎编」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Business Insider推荐过不存在的书，不得不致歉；彭博社更正了几十条AI写的错误摘要；G/O Media硬发AI写的错漏百出的文章，被全网群嘲。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过Anthropic表态了：虽然用AI写博客，但他们还在招营销、内容、编辑这些岗位呢！大家品品～</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8cdb12e-23c7-4a3c-9240-c4c752487800/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI博客昙花一现</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但，剧情反转——这博客才活了一个月就挂了！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Anthropic找了些专家和编辑来给Claude的草稿润色，确保内容靠谱，没啥AI胡扯的毛病。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们的目标是把Claude的写作能力跟人类经验结合起来。但现实给了他们一记重拳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个博客在Anthropic官网上有自己的页面，开张时发了几篇文章，SEO数据显示，一个月内就有24个网站链接到它，算是不错的成绩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可突然之间，某个周末，Anthropic直接关了博客，把网址重定向到官网首页，所有文章也全没了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先，社交媒体上的反响不太好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有些人觉得这博客就是个包装精美的营销套路，还有人吐槽Anthropic没说清楚哪些内容是Claude自己写的，哪些是人类改的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">到底是AI多厉害，还是人类在帮Claude擦屁股？</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0169c38b-ba30-4e48-a3b7-9dfa078d8100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6658322903629537\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"799\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"374\" data-imgfileid=\"505118493\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0169c38b-ba30-4e48-a3b7-9dfa078d8100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">另外，AI写作是个雷区。即使是Claude这种顶尖AI，也可能一本正经地胡说八道，搞出公关危机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Anthropic估计也怕Claude写出啥离谱的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这博客可能本来就是在试水。有消息说，他们想通过这个博客把用户想要的实用内容和营销目标结合起来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但当反馈平平，风险又摆在眼前，他们果断选择收手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">老实说，这决定挺明智——与其硬撑下去冒风险，不如及时止损。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI让工作更高效，而不是抢饭碗</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">普华永道（PwC）最新研究发现，生成式AI不仅没让我们丢工作，反而让职场来了个大升级。</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尤其在写代码、做软件这些领域，AI简直成了公司赚钱的「秘密武器」。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e40706bf-fbaa-47d6-7546-e5474f882d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6194444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"348\" data-imgfileid=\"505115294\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e40706bf-fbaa-47d6-7546-e5474f882d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">PwC分析了全球近10亿条招聘广告，发现自2022年以来，用了AI的行业，每个员工给公司赚的钱翻了三倍！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明企业在AI上砸的钱真没打水漂。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95aed067-5c2c-4931-721a-2a26cd080300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.549074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"309\" data-imgfileid=\"505115295\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95aed067-5c2c-4931-721a-2a26cd080300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">整体来看，AI带来的不是裁员潮，而是让工作模式大洗牌，工作效率、工资和技能要求都跟着涨。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这和Anthropic CEO的说法完全相反。他之前放话，说AI未来1-5年能干掉一半的入门级白领工作，让失业率飙升到10%-20%。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">新发布的Claude Code，写代码、改bug样样行，几乎能和程序员平起平坐。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d035edc-d4ec-4f5f-cea7-262119aad100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505115296\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d035edc-d4ec-4f5f-cea7-262119aad100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在流行用自然语言编程，以后估计会越来越火。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI对就业的影响有多夸张？企业为了喂饱AI，疯狂招人整理数据，数据库工程师的岗位数量去年暴增2312%，统计学家的需求也涨了382%。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Experis North America负责人Kye Mitchell表示：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI不是要抢工作，而是彻底改变工作方式。只有当一个岗位80%任务都能完全自动化时，技术才会真正取代它。但现在，大多数工作远没到这个地步。AI让我们的技能更强，干活更快，能专注在更有价值的事情上。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">PwC发现，不光高科技行业，连采矿、农业这些传统行业也在用AI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">受AI影响的行业，工资涨得比其他行业快两倍，有AI技能的人工资比同行高56%，比去年还多了31%！</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d3e5139-4b96-49e2-667f-c00c62a63900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"505115297\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d3e5139-4b96-49e2-667f-c00c62a63900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">岗位对技能的要求也在加速更新，受AI影响的岗位，技能要求的变化速度快了66%。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然整体市场不太景气，但AI相关的职位招聘还在涨。信息通信行业抢着要AI人才，建筑和医疗行业就慢半拍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在美国，和AI强相关的岗位对技能的要求却越来越高，这也说明AI在重新定义岗位，不是让人丢饭碗。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ca8fb6e-c64b-4168-6ede-42564e035000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"313\" data-imgfileid=\"505115298\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ca8fb6e-c64b-4168-6ede-42564e035000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这几年企业招人越来越不看学历，看真本事。今年4月，约一半的科技岗位招聘都没卡死本科学历。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI相关岗位，对本科学历的要求从2019年的63%降到了2024年的53%。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然学历门槛降低了，但公司都在往AI方向转型。受到不确定性影响，今年4月美国科技行业减少了21.4万个岗位。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10df20ef-8bae-4e3d-be08-5e8242db3d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5509259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"310\" data-imgfileid=\"505115299\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10df20ef-8bae-4e3d-be08-5e8242db3d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">想保住饭碗或者升职加薪，还是得赶紧学习AI技能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">不会AI，就没工作！</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多邻国（Duolingo）老板Luis von Ahn给900名员工敲了个警钟：AI现在是公司头等大事！</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他在4月备忘录里说：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">能让AI干的活，不再用外包人员；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">招聘时优先看AI技能；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">绩效评估里加入AI使用考核；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除非AI真干不了，否则不招新人。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有人吐槽AI翻译不懂人类语境，学语言怎么能少了人情味呢？有用户扬言要卸载，还有人骂公司「重AI轻员工」。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ad30688d-04d2-401b-87e7-c790df7e7a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.575925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"324\" data-imgfileid=\"505115300\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ad30688d-04d2-401b-87e7-c790df7e7a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">眼看舆论炸锅，Luis von Ahn赶紧出来救火：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">别误会，我没想让AI取代员工，我们招聘速度和以前一样。AI可以加快工作速度，质量还能更好。越早学会用AI，以后日子才越好过。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta、Shopify、Box这些大公司都在搞「AI优先」战略，包括风险评估、招聘、绩效考核。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta用AI做产品隐私风险评估，简单决策全自动化，让团队腾出精力处理复杂问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Shopify老板表示，所有人都得学怎么用AI干活，做原型、写绩效报告，招新人前必须先证明AI干不了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「AI要颠覆Shopify和我们的生活，必须all in！」直接刷屏社交媒体。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/88f8dc90-3cc0-4a15-5155-26e5207b6900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5351851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"301\" data-imgfileid=\"505115303\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/88f8dc90-3cc0-4a15-5155-26e5207b6900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在谷歌招工程师时，面试都允许用AI工具解题了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，也有公司试过之后发现不对劲。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">瑞典金融公司Klarna靠AI砍了38%的员工，AI助手顶替了800多个全职岗位，但很快发现：需要人情味和复杂判断的工作，AI根本搞不定。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d461ea92-fa31-4ab6-28f8-fee682de9d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6731481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"378\" data-imgfileid=\"505115304\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d461ea92-fa31-4ab6-28f8-fee682de9d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI不是万能的，尤其是需要细腻沟通的时候，还得靠人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在明白啥叫「技术要狠，人情味要稳」了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">CEO后来不得不承认步子迈太大了，现在一边继续投资AI，一边又招回不少零工。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">初创公司Bloomberg Beta投资人Roy Bahat表示，新公司要是不把AI当底层逻辑，根本跟不上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但关键在于怎么用，不是用AI赶人，而是让人学会跟AI配合，把重复性劳动交给机器，人去做更有创造性的事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47efb6c6-e260-4865-e30a-092b5639f000/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI正在「废掉」一代学生？</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，「会用AI」和「只会用AI」，是完全不一样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近有媒体采访了许多老师，发现现在的AI简直成了学生们的作弊神器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">各大公司都在大力向学生推广AI工具，这让那些试图限制AI在课堂上使用的老师们的努力打了水漂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">学生一登录学校的微软系统，Copilot就跳出来，怂恿你用它总结阅读材料或写草稿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">洛杉矶有个老师苦着脸说：「现在我批改的作业，差不多四成都是AI写的。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有位线上教英语的老师更崩溃：现在有些学生简直把AI当脑子用！</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f5fe3bc-a53c-40c4-cc41-448169178600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505115311\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f5fe3bc-a53c-40c4-cc41-448169178600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有次上课提问，一个学生说「老师我想想」，然后就静音了，估计是偷偷用手机搜答案呢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">等她再开口，回答得结结巴巴，明显是现查的，根本不像自己想的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究发现，用ChatGPT越多，成绩越差、记忆力越弱，连批判性思维都跟着退化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「我的学生不再思考了，他们没有兴趣爱好。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一位12年级英语教师愤怒地说，「他们没有原创的想法，只会鹦鹉学舌般重复在TikTok上听到的内容。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f79a15d6-9bff-4301-124c-d031fc7ebb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4962962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"279\" data-imgfileid=\"505115312\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f79a15d6-9bff-4301-124c-d031fc7ebb00/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">老师们气得有理，毕竟他们面对的是大公司极力推的AI热潮，完全不是他们能控制的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">说到底，当孩子们习惯了让AI代劳，失去的可能不仅仅是解题能力，更是独立思考的灵魂。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://techcrunch.com/2025/06/03/anthropics-ai-is-writing-its-own-blog-with-human-oversight/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.computerworld.com/article/4001199/pwc-genai-boosts-worker-value-wages-and-productivity-everywhere.html</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.pwc.com/gx/en/issues/artificial-intelligence/ai-jobs-barometer.html</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/2025/06/03/ai-workplace-duolingo-shopify-employees/</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章探讨 AI 内容生成的边界（Anthropic 博客失败）及 AI 对职场的双重影响（PwC 研究：效率提升、就业结构变化、技能需求激增；企业推行 AI 优先战略）和教育领域的挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章探讨 AI 内容生成的边界（Anthropic 博客失败）及 AI 对职场的双重影响（PwC 研究：效率提升、就业结构变化、技能需求激增；企业推行 AI 优先战略）和教育领域的挑战。",
  "summary": "本文通过 Anthropic 使用 Claude 生成博客内容但最终关停的案例，说明 AI 生成内容当前仍需大量人工干预和把关，且存在风险。接着引用普华永道的最新研究，指出生成式 AI 正大幅提升企业员工效率，使受影响行业人均产值显著提高，并重塑就业市场，导致特定 AI 相关岗位需求（如数据库工程师）激增，拥有 AI 技能者薪资上涨。文章进一步列举 Duolingo、Shopify 等公司积极推行“AI 优先”战略，强调掌握 AI 工具的重要性。然而，文章也提及 AI 在教育领域的负面影响，一些教师担忧学生过度依赖 AI 可能削弱独立思考和基础能力。总体来看，文章呈现了 AI 对内容创作、职场和教育的多维度影响，强调 AI 是增强人类能力而非完全取代的工具，但也伴随挑战。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 生成内容尚需大量人工干预且存在风险，需谨慎对待",
      "explanation": "Anthropic 尝试用 Claude 写博客但最终关停，表明即使是顶尖 AI 生成的内容也可能“瞎编”，需要人类专家和编辑团队进行大量审核、完善和优化，完全依赖 AI 存在公关及内容质量风险。"
    },
    {
      "point": "生成式 AI 显著提升企业效率并改变就业结构，而非普遍抢饭碗",
      "explanation": "普华永道研究显示，应用 AI 的行业员工产值大幅提升，AI 更多是改变工作方式和技能要求，对特定数据、AI 技能岗位需求激增，拥有 AI 技能者薪资更高。"
    },
    {
      "point": "企业正积极拥抱“AI 优先”战略，掌握 AI 工具成职场核心竞争力",
      "explanation": "Meta、Shopify、Duolingo 等公司将 AI 纳入招聘、绩效考核，强调员工必须学会使用 AI 工具提升效率，这成为个人在职场保持竞争力的关键。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 在教育领域带来挑战，学生过度依赖可能影响独立思考能力",
      "explanation": "部分教师担忧学生过度使用 AI 工具完成作业，将其当作“脑子”使用，可能导致学生思考能力、记忆力、批判性思维退化，失去原创想法。"
